plot: Nolan and Berlin pursue the Tarrs, their connection to the Votanis Collective exposed; Alak faces his future as a father.

Alak returns to Defiance but blames his mother for Christie's death. When they stop him from leaving with the baby, Alak tells Nolan what his parents have been up to, including blowing up the arch. With Stahma and Dalak trying to get out of town, Nolan asks T'evgin for help on fighting the Votanis Collective but gets little sympathy. Meanwhile, Rahm Tak welcomes his wife, Volubela, who tells him he's to return as he's exceeded his orders. He has other ideas.—garykmcd
